messages.message:
Hi All,
We have revamped the Passport and Drivers License applications using the build app and they are available to use on aihub.instabase.com (http://aihub.instabase.com). These apps are currently available for internal testing, Please provide feedbacks for the same.
You can find the links to application and documentation-
Passport :
Link: https://aihub.instabase.com/hub/apps/307e8e3c-4e01-4a91-a970-fa5e1e062dd2
Confluence: https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/AE/pages/2306211884/Passport+Application

US Driver's License :
Link: https://aihub.instabase.com/hub/apps/c65b56d5-31e0-4e1f-a880-03aaa321dee5
Confluence: https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/AE/pages/2306277450/US+Drivers+License+Application

Also to note, for US Driver's License , using LLM in refiner, we were getting 90% raw accuracy, whereas we are getting 93% using build app now. With introduction of validations, the validated accuracy is at 96%.
and in Passport, using refiner, we were getting 86% raw accuracy, whereas we are getting 92% using build app now. With introduction of validations, the validated accuracy is at 95%.
cc: @Shubham @smile.garg
